snippet.title: Evercade - Sunsoft Collection 1 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Sunsoft Collection 1 features 6 great games from the famous Japanese publisher!

Available September 2023
Pre-order from July 21st 2023

Find out more:  https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/sunsoft-collection-1/

Full Games List:
Aero The Acro-Bat
Arabian
Blaster Master
Blaster Master Boy
Journey to Silius
Mr. Gimmick!
